      "description": "Offering a superlative example of the E92 M3, powered by the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise engagement, coupled with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its structural integrity with the weight-saving CFRP roof panel. The paint exhibits consistent micron depth across all panels, and the subframe and suspension bushings show no signs of fatigue. An investment-grade vehicle for the enthusiast who demands peak atmospheric performance and analog feedback.",
